qDef.qDef:
Num
(
	Pick
	(
		$(v_Selected_Measure_One)
		
        ,//Quantity
		Sum([Invoice MT])
        
		,//Gross Sales
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Main Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        /1000
        
		,//Miscellaneuos Charges
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Misc Charges Provision By Value Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])  
        /1000    
        
		,//Net Sales
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])  
        /1000    
        
        ,//COGS
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
		/1000
                
        ,//COP
        (
        	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
			-
            Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
		)/1000
        
		,// Gross ASP
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Main Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        / 
        Sum([Invoice MT])
        /1000
        
		,// Unit Miscellaneuos Charges
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Misc Charges Provision By Value Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        / 
        Sum([Invoice MT])
        /1000
                        
		,// Net ASP
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        / 
        Sum([Invoice MT])
        /1000
        
		,//UCOGS
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
		/
        Sum([Invoice MT])
        /1000
                    
		,// COP/MT
		(
        	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
			-
            Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
		)
        /
        Sum([Invoice MT])
        /1000
    )
    ,
    Text
    (
		Pick
		(
			$(v_Selected_Measure_One)
			
            ,//Quantity
          	'#,##0'
            
			,//Gross Sales
          	'#,##0'
                        
			,//Miscellaneous Charges
          	'#,##0'
                        
			,//Net Sales
          	'#,##0'
                        
			,//COGS
          	'#,##0'
            
			,//COP
          	'#,##0'
            
			,//Gross ASP
			'#,##0.00'
                        
			,//Unit Miscellaneous Charges
			'#,##0.00'
                        
			,//Net ASP
			'#,##0.00'
                        
			,//Unit COGS
			'#,##0.00'
            
			,// Unit COP
			'#,##0.00'
		)
   )
   , '.' , ',' )

qAttributeExpressions.qExpression:
Pick
(
	$(v_Selected_Measure_One)
		
	,//Quantity
	if
	(
       	Sum([Invoice MT])>=0
		,rgb(0,176,80)
		,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//Gross Sales
	if
	(
       	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Main Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])<0
		,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//Miscellaneuos Charges
	rgb(151,71,6)
        
	,//Net Sales
	if
	(
       	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])<0
		,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//COGS
	rgb(151,71,6)
                
	,//COP
	if
	(
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
		>=
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
		,rgb(54,96,146)
		,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//Gross ASP
	if
	(
       	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Main Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])>=0
		,rgb(128,128,128)
       	,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//Unit Miscellaneuos Charges
	rgb(151,71,6)
                        
	,//Net ASP
	if
	(
       	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])>=0
		,rgb(128,128,128)
       	,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
        
	,//Unit COGS
	rgb(151,71,6)
                    
	,//Unit COP
	if
	(
       	Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
		>=
		Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
		,rgb(0,112,192)
		,rgb(255,0,0)
	)
)

	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
    ,
    Pick
    (
        $(v_Selected_Measure_One)
        ,//MT
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,//Amount
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
        /1000

        (
            (
              Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])

            )
        )/1000
    )
    ,
    Pick
    (
        $(v_Selected_Measure_One)

        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
